      .line
      p We are a responsible and professional team based in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam, specializing in web and mobile development with the latest Ruby on Rails and Javascript technologies. We are a group of creative experts who build full-stack solutions for our customers in multiple platforms with highly scalable back-ends and rich media front-ends. We provide fast, reliable, and professional software outsourcing, IT service consulting, website designing, and automation testing.
    .rule-content
      h4 CULTURE
      .line
      .rule-element
        = image_tag 'icon-young.png', :alt => "Golden Owl Consulting"
        .rule-info
          h5.title-rule Young Company
          p Founded in 11/2015
      .rule-element
        = image_tag 'icon-idea.png'
        .rule-info
          h5.title-rule Creactive
          p We turn our clients' creative ideas into fantastic websites
      .rule-element
        = image_tag 'icon-proactive.png'
        .rule-info
          h5.title-rule Proactive
          p We're eager to learn new technologies and make them into real life.
      .rule-element
        = image_tag 'icon-responsive.png'
